>>__ load "wordsLib"; Parse.temp_set_grammars $ valOf $ grammarDB {thyname="words"};
## `WORD_LOGIC_CONV`

``` hol4
wordsLib.WORD_LOGIC_CONV : conv
```

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Conversion based on `WORD_LOGIC_ss`.

The conversion `WORD_LOGIC_CONV` converts word logic expressions into a
canonical form.

### Example

``` hol4
>>__ load "wordsLib";

>>+ wordsLib.WORD_LOGIC_CONV “a && (b !! ~a !! c)”
```

